    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Element&nbsp;</strong>air;&nbsp;<strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>utility (Sp);&nbsp;<strong>Level&nbsp;</strong>8;&nbsp;<strong>Burn&nbsp;</strong>0</p>\n<p>By focusing on your connection to air and seeding the air around you for 10 minutes, you can create powerful weather effects, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.578t0lra5ll3aifs]{Control Weather}. You can create tornadoes or hurricane-force winds, as appropriate for the season.</p>\n<p>If you have access to the fire element, you can create hot weather, a heat wave, a thaw, or an early spring.</p>\n<p>If you have access to the water element, you can create all other types of weather listed in&nbsp;control weather.</p>",
